Class PipelineTranslatorBatch

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.beam.runners.spark.structuredstreaming.translation.PipelineTranslator
      • org.apache.beam.runners.spark.structuredstreaming.translation.batch.PipelineTranslatorBatch

  • @Internal
public class PipelineTranslatorBatch
extends PipelineTranslator
    PipelineTranslator for executing a Pipeline in Spark in batch mode. This contains only the components specific to batch: registry of batch TransformTranslator and registry lookup code.
